0009               *
0010               * ; 15  Sound player: tune source       1=ROM/RAM      0=VDP MEMORY
0011               * ; 14  Sound player: repeat tune       1=yes          0=no
0012               * ; 13  Sound player: enabled           1=yes          0=no (or pause)
